The Municipal Manager, Mr N. Pakade duly authorized by the Honourable Speaker of the King Sabata Dalindyebo Municipal Council, Councillor T. G. Maqoko gives notice in terms of Section 29(1) of Local Government Municipal Structures Act No. 117 of 1998, that a Special Council Virtual meeting of the King Sabata Dalindyebo Municipality will be held on Tuesday, 12 May 2020 starting from 10h00. In terms of Section 20(1) of the Local Government Municipal Systems Act No. 32 of 2000, members of the public and media are invited to attend the meeting, link for the virtual meeting will be available on KSD Municipality website, ksd facebook page and ksd tweeter page. I thank you. N. PAKADE (MR) MUNICIPAL MANAGER